    "Generate CodesGet buggy code C B and fixed code C F using LLM Validate ExerciseCheck if C F passes all of P's test cases and C B fails at least one Validation of the proposed failing test case is done automatically.",
    "Figure 1c shows an example where a student provides a test case meeting all required criteria.",
